address: Phường 25, Quận Bình Thạnh, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh
thought:
**Determining the New Administrative Unit for the Given Address**

Okay, so I have to figure out the new administrative unit for "Phường 25, Quận Bình Thạnh, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh." First things first, I immediately recognize "Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh" as the province.  I'll quickly reference the relevant province resolutions, but I already know that based on what I know of the area's history, the province name hasn't changed.

Now, I need to dig into the details. I'll focus my search on other resolutions specifically related to "Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh" and, more importantly, "Phường 25."  I'm looking for resolution 1685/NQ-UBTVQH15, the one dealing with administrative unit rearrangements within the city.  Bingo! Found it.

Inside that resolution, I'll zero in on "Phường 25."  And there it is: line 45 clearly states that the entirety of Phường 25, along with Phường 19 and Phường 22, will be consolidated into a new administrative unit called **phường Thạnh Mỹ Tây**.

To double-check my findings, I'll cross-reference this information with a list of new wards. Sure enough, I have a matching entry: `{"ward_code":"26956","ward_name":"Phường Thạnh Mỹ Tây","province_name":"Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh"}`. Perfect!

The resolution is incredibly clear and direct in this case, making this a highly confident determination.  The old "Phường 25" is now part of the new "Phường Thạnh Mỹ Tây." That's my answer.
